select `idSeance`, `dateSeance`, `idTypeProjet`, `id_google_seance`, `idDossier`, `heureDebut`, `heureFin`, `idSalle`, `v_seances`.`idProjet` as `idProjet`, `project_reference`, `salle_name`, `salle_quartier`, `project_title`, `project_description`, `idModule`, `module_name`, `modalite`, `vcd`.`ville_name`, `vcd`.`vi_code_postal`, COUNT(*) AS nb_seances, GROUP_CONCAT( dateSeance, 'T', heureDebut) AS seance_start, GROUP_CONCAT( dateSeance, 'T', heureFin) AS seance_end from `v_seances` left join `project_sub_contracts` as `psc` on `v_seances`.`idProjet` = `psc`.`idProjet` left join `customers` as `sub` on `psc`.`idSubContractor` = `sub`.`idCustomer` left join `customers` as `ce` on `v_seances`.`idCfp` = `ce`.`idCustomer` left join `lieux` as `li` on `li`.`idLieu` = `v_seances`.`idLieu` left join `ville_codeds` as `vcd` on `vcd`.`id` = `li`.`idVilleCoded` where (`idCfp` = 2 or `psc`.`idSubContractor` = 2) and `project_is_trashed` = 0 group by DATE(dateSeance), `idModule`, `module_name`, `modalite` order by DATE(dateSeance)
